at the bottom of the pyramid again?

00:06:16.642 --> 00:06:18.177 line:95%,end
-HOLLY: Aw. I'm sorry.
-Surprise, surprise!

00:06:18.244 --> 00:06:19.212 line:95%,end
MELISSA: But you know what?

00:06:19.278 --> 00:06:20.413 line:95%,end
I just want to tell you something.

00:06:20.480 --> 00:06:23.616 line:95%,end
I think that her solo was the best
she's ever done any solo.

00:06:23.683 --> 00:06:24.684 line:95%,end
Didn't you?

00:06:25.184 --> 00:06:26.819 line:95%,end
She acted so well in it.

00:06:26.886 --> 00:06:28.187 line:95%,end
Especially in her age category.

00:06:28.254 --> 00:06:29.589 line:95%,end
I mean, you have to do...

00:06:29.655 --> 00:06:31.791 line:95%,end
-MELISSA: She made me smile.
-...some kind of dancing in it.

