-CHRISTI: She's not gonna--

00:06:49.809 --> 00:06:51.210 line:95%,end
-HOLLY: I would be offended.
-I don't think we're ever gonna

00:06:51.277 --> 00:06:52.111 line:95%,end
see Cathy again.

00:06:52.178 --> 00:06:53.980 line:95%,end
-I think Cathy hit the road. No.
-HOLLY: You don't think so?

00:06:54.046 --> 00:06:57.049 line:95%,end
(playful music playing)

00:06:58.317 --> 00:07:01.687 line:95%,end
CATHY: <i>As I was driving home</i>
<i>from Pittsburgh, I was elated.</i>

00:07:01.754 --> 00:07:06.426 line:95%,end
<i>I could not get far enough</i>
<i>away from the Abby Lee Dance Company.</i>

00:07:07.093 --> 00:07:12.899 line:5%,start
I was really happy to see the Ohio sign,
Ohio welcomes you.

00:07:12.965 --> 00:07:14.434 line:95%,end
I couldn't have been happier.

00:07:14.500 --> 00:07:17.503 line:95%,end
(foreboding music playing)

00:07:23.476 --> 00:07:28.147 line:95%,end
CATHY: First of all, ladies, gentleman,
I'm so happy to be back.

00:07:28.214 --> 00:07:32.852 line:95%,end
As you know, I was splitting
my time from the Abby Lee Dance Center

00:07:32.919 --> 00:07:34.086 line:95%,end
and Candy Apples.

00:07:34.153 --> 00:07:36.189 line:95%,end
I wanted Vivi to get
a little bit more experience

00:07:36.255 --> 00:07:39.192 line:95%,end
because she's starting
to get on that brink of titles,

00:07:39.258 --> 00:07:44.464 line:95%,end
and with me being her mom,
I wanted to let her go to a dance teacher

00:07:44.530 --> 00:07:47.333 line:95%,end
