truly am going to do,

00:08:13.559 --> 00:08:14.894 line:95%,end
and I'm gonna put it in motion.

00:08:14.961 --> 00:08:17.497 line:95%,end
And that is that Candy Apples
Dance Center is going

00:08:17.563 --> 00:08:19.799 line:95%,end
to meet up with the Abby Lee dancers
in Hollywood,

00:08:19.866 --> 00:08:21.601 line:95%,end
<i>and we're gonna go head to head.</i>

00:08:21.667 --> 00:08:23.836 line:95%,end
There are going to be
three of you that get

00:08:23.903 --> 00:08:25.538 line:95%,end
to go to Hollywood, California.

00:08:25.605 --> 00:08:28.608 line:95%,end
(tense music playing)


00:08:29.609 --> 00:08:33.112 line:95%,end
CATHY: Justice, Justice,
you are going to go to Hollywood.

00:08:33.179 --> 00:08:36.115 line:95%,end
(tense music playing)

00:08:36.182 --> 00:08:39.552 line:95%,end
CATHY:
Vivi, Vivi had the inside scoop there.

00:08:39.619 --> 00:08:41.287 line:95%,end
You are going to go to Hollywood.

00:08:42.355 --> 00:08:45.291 line:95%,end
And our third Apple,
Taylor (indistinct)

00:08:45.358 --> 00:08:48.160 line:95%,end
Taylor, you will be doing
a contemporary piece

00:08:48.794 --> 00:08:51.898 line:95%,end
and competing against one
of Abby's so-called finest.

00:08:51.964 --> 00:08:53.132 line:95%,end
