00:10:51.083 --> 00:10:54.687 line:95%,end
MELISSA: <i>She actually handed</i>
<i>each person their own sin</i>

00:10:54.754 --> 00:10:57.757 line:95%,end
<i>so they can act it out on stage,</i>
